msgstr "API"

msgid "Input"
msgstr "输入"

msgid "Automatic mode"
msgstr "自动模式"

msgid "Record requirement"
msgstr "记录要求"

msgid "Recovery"
msgstr "恢复"

msgid "`ray.klein.from_items(items)`"
msgstr "`ray.klein.from_items(items)`"

msgid "Iterable accepted by Ray Data"
msgstr "Ray Data 接受的可迭代对象"

msgid "Batch"
msgstr "批处理"

msgid "Ray Data-compatible items"
msgstr "与 Ray Data 兼容的元素"

msgid "Ray Data retry semantics"
msgstr "Ray Data 重试语义"

msgid "`ray.klein.from_values(*values)`"
msgstr "`ray.klein.from_values(*values)`"

msgid "Positional values"
msgstr "位置参数值"

msgid "Streaming"
msgstr "流处理"

msgid "Every value must be a mapping"
msgstr "每个值都必须是映射"

msgid "Restores the next unread index"
msgstr "恢复下一个未读取的索引"

msgid "`ray.klein.from_ray_dataset(dataset)`"
msgstr "`ray.klein.from_ray_dataset(dataset)`"

msgid "Existing Ray `Dataset`"
msgstr "现有 Ray `Dataset`"

msgid "Dataset schema"
msgstr "Dataset schema"

msgid ""
"`from_items` has both a native collection source and a Ray Data lowering,"
" so automatic mode selects batch under the default UDF exception policy. "
"Setting `udf.ignore-exception=true` or explicitly forcing streaming "
"selects the native runtime, where values must be mappings because the "
"native `SourceContext.collect()` contract accepts mapping records."
msgstr ""
"`from_items` 同时提供原生集合数据源和 Ray Data 下沉实现，因此在默认 UDF "
"异常策略下，自动模式会选择批处理。设置 `udf.ignore-exception=true` "
"或显式强制使用流处理会选择原生运行时；此时值必须是映射，因为原生 "
"`SourceContext.collect()` 契约只接受映射记录。"

msgid "Create a bounded collection"
msgstr "创建有界集合"

msgid "Use an existing Dataset without materializing it on the driver:"
msgstr "使用现有 Dataset，而不在 Driver 上将其物化："

msgid ""
"Both forms are batch-only in normal use and can be followed by [Ray Data "
"operations](ray-data.md)."
msgstr "正常使用时，这两种形式都仅支持批处理，后续可以接续 [Ray Data 操作](ray-data.md)。"

msgid "Create a finite streaming source"
msgstr "创建有限流 Source"

msgid ""
"`from_values` intentionally has no Ray Data lowering, so it selects "
"native streaming execution. Its checkpoint state stores the next value "
"index. After recovery, values before that index are not emitted again by "
"the source, though downstream external sinks can still have their own "
"replay semantics."
msgstr ""
"`from_values` 有意不提供 Ray Data "
"lowering，因此会选择原生流处理执行。其检查点状态存储下一个值的索引。恢复后，Source 不会再次发出该索引之前的值，但下游外部 Sink"
" 仍可能具有自己的重放语义。"

msgid "Configuration and limits"
msgstr "配置与限制"

msgid ""
"These APIs have no connector-specific configuration. `from_values` "
"accepts only an optional operator `name`; `from_items` and "
"`from_ray_dataset` follow their public API signatures. Job-wide runtime "
"and checkpoint settings are in the [configuration reference"
"](../configuration-reference.md)."
msgstr ""
"这些 API 没有 Connector 专用配置。`from_values` 仅接受可选的 Operator "
"`name`；`from_items` 和 `from_ray_dataset` 遵循各自的公开 API "
"签名。作业级运行时和检查点设置请参阅[配置参考](../configuration-reference.md)。"

msgid ""
"The collection is serialized with the submitted job, so large local "
"datasets increase driver memory and submission cost. Store production-"
"scale data in a distributed system and use a dedicated connector."
msgstr ""
"集合会随提交的作业一起序列化，因此大型本地数据集会增加 Driver 内存占用和提交开销。请将生产规模的数据存储在分布式系统中，并使用专用 "
"Connector。"

msgid ""
"Inspect Klein for Ray batch and streaming records with the console and "
"print connector."
msgstr "使用 console 和 print Connector 查看 Klein for Ray 的批处理与流处理记录。"

msgid "Console and print"
msgstr "Console 与 print"

msgid ""
"The console sink is a diagnostic connector for examples and local "
"debugging. It prints records to standard output and provides no external "
"durability or deduplication."
msgstr "Console Sink 是用于示例和本地调试的诊断 Connector。它将记录打印到标准输出，不提供外部持久性或去重。"

msgid "Use the DataStream API"
msgstr "使用 DataStream API"

