msgid "**Ray Data streaming**"
msgstr "**Ray Data 流处理**"

msgid ""
"`stream.data.with_column(name, expr)` and `stream.data.filter(expr=expr)`"
" support streaming. Other Ray Data operations are batch-only; Klein's "
"native filesystem writers and `stream.write_sql` support streaming "
"separately."
msgstr ""
"`stream.data.with_column(name, expr)` 和 `stream.data.filter(expr=expr)` "
"支持流处理。其他 Ray Data 操作仅支持批处理；Klein 的原生 Filesystem Writer 和 "
"`stream.write_sql` 分别支持流处理。"

msgid "**Redis transformations**"
msgstr "**Redis 转换**"

msgid ""
"Redis lookup and missing-key transforms work in both modes; Redis output "
"is a native streaming sink."
msgstr "Redis Lookup 和缺失键 Transform 可在两种模式下工作；Redis 输出是原生流处理 Sink。"

msgid "Choose a connector"
msgstr "选择 Connector"

msgid ""
"For bounded data already supported by Ray Data, use the dynamic [Ray Data"
" adapter](ray-data.md). Klein preserves Ray Data's public arguments "
"instead of duplicating them."
msgstr ""
"对于 Ray Data 已支持的有界数据，请使用动态 [Ray Data 适配器](ray-data.md)。Klein 会保留 Ray Data"
" 的公开参数，而不会重复定义。"

msgid ""
"For a long-running event log, use [Kafka](kafka.md). Continuous input is "
"checkpoint-aware; output is at-least-once."
msgstr "对于长期运行的事件日志，请使用 [Kafka](kafka.md)。连续输入感知检查点；输出具有 at-least-once 语义。"

msgid ""
"For an existing remoting-protocol Apache RocketMQ deployment, use "
"[RocketMQ](rocketmq.md) and review its broker-managed recovery boundary."
msgstr ""
"对于现有的 remoting-protocol Apache RocketMQ 部署，请使用 "
"[RocketMQ](rocketmq.md)，并查看其由 Broker 管理的恢复边界。"

msgid ""
"For MySQL CDC already published by Canal, use Kafka with the [Canal JSON "
"format](canal.md). FlatMessage JSON is decoded into native Klein "
"changelog rows without introducing another connector."
msgstr ""
"对于已由 Canal 发布的 MySQL CDC，请将 Kafka 与 [Canal JSON "
"格式](canal.md)配合使用。FlatMessage JSON 会解码为原生 Klein 变更日志行，而无需引入其他 Connector。"

msgid ""
"For checkpoint-transactional output, use [filesystem](filesystem.md). "
"Final part files become visible only after their Klein checkpoint is "
"durable."
msgstr ""
"对于具备检查点事务语义的输出，请使用 [Filesystem](filesystem.md)。最终 part 文件只会在对应 Klein "
"检查点持久化后可见。"

msgid ""
"For an existing lakehouse table, use [Iceberg](iceberg.md). Batch mode "
"keeps Ray Data's append/overwrite/upsert behavior; streaming mode appends"
" snapshots only after a Klein checkpoint becomes durable."
msgstr ""
"对于现有 Lakehouse 表，请使用 [Iceberg](iceberg.md)。批处理模式保留 Ray Data 的 "
"append/overwrite/upsert 行为；流处理模式只会在 Klein 检查点持久化后追加 snapshot。"

msgid ""
"For enrichment or a materialized key/value output, use [Redis](redis.md),"
" and account for its external at-least-once semantics."
msgstr "对于数据扩充或物化键值输出，请使用 [Redis](redis.md)，并考虑其外部 at-least-once 语义。"

msgid "For development-only inspection, use [console](console.md)."
msgstr "若仅在开发时查看数据，请使用 [Console](console.md)。"

msgid "To integrate another system, implement a [custom connector](custom.md)."
msgstr "如需集成其他系统，请实现[自定义 Connector](custom.md)。"

msgid "Execution-mode rule"
msgstr "执行模式规则"

msgid ""
"In `auto` mode, an unbounded source, any graph vertex without a batch "
"lowering, or `udf.ignore-exception=true` selects streaming; only a fully "
"batch-lowerable, bounded graph with that policy disabled selects batch. A"
" native `SourceFunction` or `SinkFunction` without a lowering therefore "
"selects streaming automatically, even when the source is bounded. See "
"[Configuration](../configuration.md) for explicit mode selection and [Ray"
" Data interoperation](../ray-data-interop.md) for the lowering model."
msgstr ""
"在 `auto` 模式下，无界数据源、任何缺少批处理下沉实现的计算图顶点，或 "
"`udf.ignore-exception=true` 都会使运行时选择流处理；只有关闭该策略且整个"
"有界图均可下沉为批处理时，才选择批处理。因此，未提供下沉实现的原生 "
"`SourceFunction` 或 `SinkFunction` 会自动选择流处理，即使数据源有界也是"
"如此。有关显式选择模式的方法，请参阅[配置](../configuration.md)；有关下沉"
"模型，请参阅 [Ray Data 互操作](../ray-data-interop.md)。"

msgid ""
"Configure Klein for Ray Kafka bounded and continuous input, output, "
"checkpoint offsets, and Table DDL."
msgstr "配置 Klein for Ray Kafka 的有界与连续输入、输出、检查点 offset 和 Table DDL。"

msgid "Kafka"
msgstr "Kafka"

msgid ""
"Klein reads Kafka either as a bounded Ray Data input or as a native "
"continuous source. Kafka output lowers to Ray Data in batch and uses a "
"native producer in streaming. Install the connector dependency with:"
msgstr ""
"Klein 将 Kafka 读取为有界 Ray Data 输入或原生连续 Source。Kafka 输出在批处理模式下 lowering 到 "
"Ray Data，在流处理模式下使用原生 Producer。请安装 Connector 依赖："

msgid "Read Kafka"
msgstr "读取 Kafka"

msgid ""
"Set `trigger=\"once\"` for bounded Ray Data input or `\"continuous\"` for"
" a long-running checkpoint-aware source."
msgstr ""
"对于有界 Ray Data 输入，请设置 `trigger=\"once\"`；对于长期运行且感知检查点的 Source，请设置 "
"`\"continuous\"`。"

