msgstr "整数起始 offset 必须为非负数。无时区的 `datetime` 会解释为 UTC。分区专用映射的格式如下："

msgid ""
"Continuous `timeout_ms`, `partition_discovery_interval_ms`, and "
"`max_batch_size` must be positive integers when set. Topic names, broker "
"addresses, and configured partition IDs are validated before polling."
msgstr ""
"连续模式下，`timeout_ms`、`partition_discovery_interval_ms` 和 `max_batch_size` "
"在设置时必须为正整数。轮询前会验证 topic 名称、Broker 地址和已配置的分区 ID。"

msgid "Input record schema"
msgstr "输入记录 schema"

msgid ""
