msgid ""
"Deserialize `key` and `value` explicitly in the next transform so schema "
"and error handling remain application-owned."
msgstr "请在下一个 Transform 中显式反序列化 `key` 和 `value`，使 schema 和错误处理仍由应用控制。"

msgid ""
"For an unchained source boundary, all valid raw records returned by one "
"Kafka poll are emitted as one columnar transport block. A chained row "
"operator still receives ordinary rows, because chaining already removes "
"the actor RPC. Poll offsets are advanced before the block and any "
"checkpoint barrier is ordered after it."
msgstr ""
"对于未 Chaining 的 Source 边界，一次 Kafka 轮询返回的所有有效原始记录会作为一个列式传输 Block "
"发出。Chaining 的行 Operator 仍会接收普通行，因为 Chaining 已经消除了 Actor RPC。轮询 offset 会在该"
" Block 前推进，所有检查点 Barrier 都排在其后。"

msgid ""
"For Canal Server FlatMessage JSON, select the [Canal JSON value "
"format](canal.md) to obtain INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE changelog rows with "
"checkpoint-safe recovery inside multi-row Kafka messages."
msgstr ""
"对于 Canal Server FlatMessage JSON，请选择 [Canal JSON 值格式](canal.md)，以获取 "
"INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE 变更日志行，并在包含多行的 Kafka 消息内部实现检查点安全恢复。"

msgid "Partition assignment and recovery"
msgstr "分区分配与恢复"

msgid ""
"The continuous source sorts discovered topic partitions and assigns them "
"by partition index modulo source parallelism. It periodically discovers "
"new partitions without restarting the job. Empty polls still report "
"source idleness so time-based checkpoints and watermarks can progress."
msgstr ""
"连续 Source 会对发现的 topic 分区排序，并按分区索引对 Source "
"并行度取模来分配分区。它会定期发现新分区，无需重启作业。空轮询仍会报告 Source 空闲，使基于时间的检查点和 Watermark 能够推进。"

msgid "Resume position is chosen in this order:"
msgstr "恢复位置按以下顺序选择："

msgid "offsets restored from a durable Klein checkpoint;"
msgstr "从持久 Klein 检查点恢复的 offset；"

msgid "positions already held by the running source;"
msgstr "运行中 Source 已持有的位置；"

msgid "committed offsets for the configured Kafka consumer group;"
msgstr "已配置 Kafka 消费组的已提交 offset；"

msgid "`start_offset`."
msgstr "`start_offset`。"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Klein forces `enable.auto.offset.store=false` and disables automatic "
"commits; `enable.auto.commit=true` is rejected. If `group.id` is absent, "
"Klein uses `ray-klein-{job_id}`. It commits Kafka group offsets only "
"after the corresponding Klein checkpoint is durable and retries a failed "
"commit. This prevents the consumer group from moving ahead of recoverable"
" Klein state."
msgstr ""
"Klein 会强制设置 `enable.auto.offset.store=false` "
"并禁用自动提交；`enable.auto.commit=true` 会被拒绝。如果没有 `group.id`，Klein 使用 `ray-"
"klein-{job_id}`。它只会在对应 Klein 检查点持久化后提交 Kafka 消费组 "
"offset，并会重试失败的提交。这可防止消费组位置超前于可恢复的 Klein 状态。"

msgid "Write Kafka"
msgstr "写入 Kafka"

msgid "Output options"
msgstr "输出选项"

msgid "Exactly one output topic."
msgstr "恰好一个输出 topic。"

msgid "Broker addresses; overrides any same property in `producer_config`."
msgstr "Broker 地址；会覆盖 `producer_config` 中的同名属性。"

msgid "`key_field`"
msgstr "`key_field`"

msgid "Optional mapping field used as the Kafka key."
msgstr "用作 Kafka key 的可选映射字段。"

msgid "`key_serializer`"
msgstr "`key_serializer`"

msgid "`\"string\"`"
msgstr "`\"string\"`"

msgid "`string`, `json`, or `bytes`."
msgstr "`string`、`json` 或 `bytes`。"

msgid "`value_serializer`"
msgstr "`value_serializer`"

msgid "`\"json\"`"
msgstr "`\"json\"`"

msgid "`json`, `string`, or `bytes`."
msgstr "`json`、`string` 或 `bytes`。"

msgid "`producer_config`"
msgstr "`producer_config`"

msgid "Additional Confluent producer properties."
msgstr "额外的 Confluent Producer 属性。"

msgid ""
"Ray Data batch task arguments; `num_cpus` and `num_gpus` also size native"
" sink tasks."
msgstr "Ray Data 批处理 Task 参数；`num_cpus` 和 `num_gpus` 也用于确定原生 Sink Task 的资源大小。"

msgid "Sink parallelism."
msgstr "Sink 并行度。"

msgid ""
"`json` uses JSON encoding, `string` uses `str(value).encode(\"utf-8\")`, "
"and `bytes` preserves an existing `bytes` value but UTF-8 encodes "
"`str(value)` for other types. If `key_field` is absent or its value is "
"`None`, the producer sends no Kafka key. The value serializer receives "
"the whole record mapping."
msgstr ""
"`json` 使用 JSON 编码，`string` 使用 `str(value).encode(\"utf-8\")`，`bytes` "
"会保留现有 `bytes` 值，但对其他类型的 `str(value)` 使用 UTF-8 编码。如果没有 `key_field` 或其值为 "
"`None`，Producer 不会发送 Kafka key。Value Serializer 接收完整的记录映射。"

msgid ""
"The streaming producer flushes outstanding deliveries at checkpoint "
"barriers and waits for acknowledgements, but it does not use Kafka "
"transactions. Output is therefore **at-least-once**: recovery can replay "
"records that Kafka already accepted before the failed checkpoint became "
"durable. Use an idempotent downstream key/version design when duplicates "
"matter."
msgstr ""
"流处理 Producer 会在检查点 Barrier 处刷新未完成的交付并等待确认，但不会使用 Kafka 事务。因此，输出具有 **at-"
"least-once** 语义：恢复可能重放 Kafka "
"已接受、但失败检查点持久化之前的记录。如果重复记录会造成影响，请在下游采用幂等的键/版本设计。"

msgid ""
"The connector identifier is `kafka`. `consumer_config`, "
"`producer_config`, and `ray_remote_args` are JSON strings in SQL:"
msgstr ""
"Connector 标识符为 `kafka`。在 SQL 中，`consumer_config`、`producer_config` 和 "
"`ray_remote_args` 是 JSON 字符串："

msgid ""
"Source tables require `topic` or `topics` plus `bootstrap_servers`. Sink "
"tables require exactly one topic. Supported keys are the snake-case API "
"names shown in the option tables: `trigger`, offsets, consumer/producer "
"config, resources, block/concurrency settings, discovery and batch size, "
"`format`, and serializers. Format-specific source options use a prefix "
"such as `canal-json.include-metadata`. See [SQL and Table DDL](../sql.md)"
" for statement syntax and row-kind validation."
msgstr ""
"Source 表需要 `topic` 或 `topics`，以及 `bootstrap_servers`。Sink 表要求恰好一个 "
"topic。支持的键是选项表中所示的 snake-case API 名称：`trigger`、offset、Consumer/Producer "
"配置、资源、Block/并发度设置、发现与批次大小、`format` 和 Serializer。格式专用 Source 选项使用 `canal-"
"json.include-metadata` 之类的前缀。有关语句语法和行类型验证，请参阅 [SQL 与 Table "
"DDL](../sql.md)。"

msgid "Operational notes"
msgstr "运维说明"

msgid ""
"Keep Klein checkpoint storage durable; Kafka offset commits alone cannot "
"restore operator state."
msgstr "请确保 Klein 检查点存储持久可靠；仅提交 Kafka offset 无法恢复 Operator 状态。"

msgid ""
"Use a stable `group.id` when recovery must survive a new Klein job "
"identity."
msgstr "如果恢复需要跨越新的 Klein 作业标识，请使用稳定的 `group.id`。"

msgid ""
"Scale continuous source concurrency no higher than useful topic-partition"
" parallelism. Idle subtasks do not increase Kafka throughput."
msgstr "连续 Source 并发度不应超过有效的 topic 分区并行度。空闲 Subtask 不会提高 Kafka 吞吐量。"

msgid ""
"Monitor checkpoint duration, consumer lag, records consumed/produced, and"
" producer error metrics described in "
"[Observability](../observability.md)."
msgstr ""
"请监控[可观测性](../observability.md)中说明的检查点耗时、Consumer Lag、消费/生产记录数和 Producer "
"错误指标。"

msgid ""
"Use public Ray Data readers, transforms, consumers, and writers through "
"Klein for Ray."
msgstr "通过 Klein for Ray 使用公开的 Ray Data Reader、Transform、Consumer 和 Writer。"

msgid "Ray Data"
msgstr "Ray Data"

msgid ""
"The Ray Data adapter exposes public Ray Data `Dataset` factories and "
"methods as bounded Klein sources and operations. It is the broadest batch"
" connector: when Ray Data adds a public reader or writer, a compatible "
"Klein installation can expose it without a Klein wrapper release."
msgstr ""
"Ray Data 适配器将公开的 Ray Data `Dataset` Factory 和方法公开为有界 Klein Source "
"和操作。它是覆盖面最广的批处理 Connector：当 Ray Data 添加公开 Reader 或 Writer 时，兼容的 Klein "
"安装无需发布 Klein 封装版本即可公开它。"

msgid "Availability and execution mode"
msgstr "可用性与执行模式"

msgid ""
"Ray Data sources, general `stream.data` transforms, and `stream.data` "
"consumers are batch-only. The expression forms "
"`stream.data.with_column(name, expr)` and `stream.data.filter(expr=expr)`"
" are dual-mode: batch execution delegates to Ray Data unchanged, while "
"streaming execution uses Klein's native expression operator. `download()`"
" runs with bounded ordered concurrency and backpressure."
msgstr ""
"Ray Data Source、通用 `stream.data` Transform 和 `stream.data` Consumer "
"仅支持批处理。表达式形式 `stream.data.with_column(name, expr)` 和 "
"`stream.data.filter(expr=expr)` 支持双模式：批处理执行会原样委托给 Ray Data，流处理执行则使用 Klein"
" 的原生表达式 Operator。`download()` 以有界有序并发和背压运行。"

msgid ""
"Check availability before relying on an API that differs across Ray "
"versions:"
msgstr "在依赖不同 Ray 版本间存在差异的 API 前，请先检查可用性："

msgid ""
"Klein supports the Ray version range stated in "
"[Compatibility](../compatibility.md). Public Ray Data APIs outside that "
"range are not compatibility guarantees."
msgstr ""
"Klein 支持[兼容性](../compatibility.md)中声明的 Ray 版本范围。该范围之外的公开 Ray Data API "
"不属于兼容性保证。"

msgid "Read data"
msgstr "读取数据"

msgid ""
"Call a public Ray Data factory directly from `ray.klein` or through "
"`source`:"
msgstr "可直接从 `ray.klein` 或通过 `source` 调用公开的 Ray Data factory："

msgid ""
"You can also pass a public Ray Data factory callable instead of its name."
" Klein preserves the installed function's signature and documentation, "
"and forwards all arguments to Ray Data. Consult the matching [Ray Data "
"input API](https://docs.ray.io/en/latest/data/api/input_output.html) for "
"connector-specific options, credentials, schemas, and return values."
msgstr ""
"也可以传入公开的 Ray Data Factory Callable，而不是其名称。Klein 会保留已安装函数的签名和文档，并将所有参数转发给 "
"Ray Data。有关 Connector 专用选项、凭据、schema 和返回值，请查阅对应的 [Ray Data 输入 "
"API](https://docs.ray.io/en/latest/data/api/input_output.html)。"

msgid "Transform data"
msgstr "转换数据"

msgid "`stream.data` dynamically exposes public `Dataset` methods:"
msgstr "`stream.data` 动态公开 `Dataset` 的公开方法："

msgid ""
"Use `transform` when an operation needs more than one stream or is easier"
" to express as a Dataset-to-Dataset function:"
msgstr "当操作需要多个 Stream，或更适合表达为 Dataset 到 Dataset 的函数时，请使用 `transform`："

msgid ""
"The callable passed to `transform` must return exactly one Ray `Dataset`."
" Additional `DataStream` arguments become graph dependencies and are "
"replaced with their lowered Datasets at execution time."
msgstr ""
"传给 `transform` 的 Callable 必须恰好返回一个 Ray `Dataset`。额外的 `DataStream` "
"参数会成为图依赖，并在执行时替换为 lowering 后的 Dataset。"

msgid "Consume or write data"
msgstr "消费或写入数据"

msgid ""
"Public terminal Dataset methods are available through `stream.data`, "
"including writers supported by the installed Ray version:"
msgstr "可通过 `stream.data` 使用公开的终结 Dataset 方法，包括已安装 Ray 版本支持的 Writer："

msgid ""
"Unlike `transform`, `consume` may return any value accepted by the "
"underlying terminal operation. The result is represented as a Klein sink "
"and becomes part of the submitted job."
msgstr ""
"与 `transform` 不同，`consume` 可以返回底层终结操作接受的任意值。结果会表示为 Klein "
"Sink，并成为已提交作业的一部分。"

msgid ""
"For JSON, CSV, and Parquet, `stream.write_json`, `write_csv`, and "
"`write_parquet` provide a stable Klein entry point that lowers to Ray "
"Data in batch and uses checkpoint-transactional native output in "
"streaming. See [Filesystem](filesystem.md) before choosing between the "
"APIs."
msgstr ""
"对于 JSON、CSV 和 Parquet，`stream.write_json`、`write_csv` 和 `write_parquet` "
"提供稳定的 Klein 入口：在批处理模式下降低为 Ray Data，在流处理模式下使用具备检查点事务语义的原生输出。在这些 API "
"之间进行选择前，请参阅 [Filesystem](filesystem.md)。"

msgid ""
"`stream.write_sql(sql, connection_factory, ray_remote_args=None, "
"concurrency=None)` is also available with the same arguments as "
"`ray.data.Dataset.write_sql`. Batch execution uses Ray Data's writer. "
"Streaming execution owns one DB-API 2.0 connection per sink subtask, "
"preserves the first record's column order, and commits `executemany` "
"batches of up to 128 rows at full batches and checkpoint flushes."
msgstr ""
"还可使用 `stream.write_sql(sql, connection_factory, ray_remote_args=None, "
"concurrency=None)`，其参数与 `ray.data.Dataset.write_sql` 相同。批处理执行使用 Ray Data "
"Writer。流处理执行为每个 Sink Subtask 持有一个 DB-API 2.0 "
"连接，保留第一条记录的列顺序，并在批次填满和检查点刷新时提交最多 128 行的 `executemany` 批次。"

msgid ""
"Streaming SQL output is at-least-once: a database commit can succeed "
"before the matching Klein checkpoint becomes durable. Use an idempotent "
"statement or database-native upsert when replayed rows must not create "
"duplicates."
msgstr ""
"流处理 SQL 输出具有 at-least-once 语义：数据库提交可能在匹配的 Klein "
"检查点持久化前成功。如果重放行不能产生重复数据，请使用幂等语句或数据库原生 upsert。"

msgid "Adapt an existing Dataset"
msgstr "适配现有 Dataset"

msgid ""
"Use `from_ray_dataset` when another library has already constructed a "
"Dataset:"
msgstr "当其他库已经构造了 Dataset 时，请使用 `from_ray_dataset`："

msgid ""
"The Dataset remains bounded and batch-only. Klein does not collect it "
"into the driver or convert it to a native streaming source."
msgstr "该 Dataset 保持有界且仅支持批处理。Klein 不会将其收集到 Driver，也不会将其转换为原生流处理 Source。"

msgid "Configuration and guarantees"
msgstr "配置与保证"

msgid ""
"There are no Ray Data connector-wide Klein options. Pass connector and "
"resource arguments to the selected Ray Data method. Klein's job-wide "
"`execution.runtime.mode`, retry, and Ray initialization options still "
"apply; see the [configuration reference](../configuration-reference.md)."
msgstr ""
"没有适用于整个 Ray Data Connector 的 Klein 选项。请将 Connector 和资源参数传给所选 Ray Data "
"方法。Klein 作业级 `execution.runtime.mode`、重试和 Ray 初始化选项仍然适用；请参阅[配置参考"
"](../configuration-reference.md)。"

msgid ""
"Except for the native `stream.write_sql` path described above, data "
"partitioning, retries, commit behavior, and filesystem semantics are "
"those of the invoked public Ray Data operation. They are not Klein "
"streaming checkpoints. Use a transactional native connector when the "
"external system must commit only after a Klein checkpoint becomes "
"durable."
msgstr ""
"除上述原生 `stream.write_sql` 路径外，数据分区、重试、提交行为和文件系统语义均由所调用的公开 Ray Data "
"操作决定；它们不是 Klein 流处理检查点。如果外部系统必须在 Klein 检查点持久化后才提交，请使用事务型原生 Connector。"

msgid ""
"Run a connected Klein for Ray transformation region behind Ray Serve "
"through an embedded proxy client."
msgstr "通过嵌入式 Proxy Client，在 Ray Serve 后运行相连的 Klein for Ray Transform 区域。"

msgid "Ray Serve execution integration"
msgstr "Ray Serve 执行集成"

msgid ""
"Ray Serve is an optional execution integration, not a data source or "
"sink. It moves one connected transform region behind a Serve deployment "
"and replaces that region in the Klein graph with an asynchronous HTTP "
"proxy client. Use it for independently deployed model or inference "
"transforms in batch or streaming graphs."
msgstr ""
"Ray Serve 是可选的执行集成，而不是数据 Source 或 Sink。它会将一个相连的 Transform 区域移到 Serve "
"Deployment 后，并在 Klein 图中用异步 HTTP Proxy Client "
"替换该区域。可将其用于批处理或流处理图中独立部署的模型或推理 Transform。"

msgid "Install the optional dependencies:"
msgstr "安装可选依赖："

msgid "Mark a Serve region"
msgstr "标记 Serve 区域"

msgid ""
"Mark synchronous `map_batches` transforms in the original workflow. The "
"current Serve runtime accepts only NumPy/default batch format; other "
"transform kinds, async or generator callables, and pandas/Arrow batches "
"are rejected while the logical graph is built:"
msgstr ""
"在原始工作流中标记同步 `map_batches` 转换。当前 Serve 运行时仅接受 "
"NumPy/默认批次格式；构建逻辑图时会拒绝其他转换类型、异步或生成器可调用对象，以及 pandas/Arrow 批次："

msgid ""
"All marked nodes in a job must form exactly one connected linear chain. A"
" branch or merge inside the marked region, or two disconnected marked "
"regions, is rejected during graph construction. External inputs may only "
"enter the chain's head, and external outputs may only leave its tail; "
"tail fan-out is supported. Functions, constructor arguments, and returned"
" values must remain serializable and compatible with the selected "
"operator's batch contract."
msgstr "作业中所有已标记节点必须恰好形成一条相连的线性链。在已标记区域内部出现分支或合并，或存在两个互不相连的已标记区域，都会在构图时被拒绝。外部输入只能进入链首，外部输出只能从链尾离开；支持链尾扇出。函数、构造参数和返回值必须保持可序列化，并与所选算子的批次约定兼容。"

msgid ""
"In a streaming graph the proxy is an ordinary transform operator, but the"
" remote HTTP service does not participate in Klein's checkpoint protocol."
msgstr "在流处理图中，Proxy 是普通 Transform Operator，但远程 HTTP 服务不参与 Klein 的检查点协议。"

msgid "Deploy the operator chain"
msgstr "部署 Operator Chain"

msgid ""
"The Serve deployment imports Klein's bound application and receives the "
"same workflow path as user configuration:"
msgstr "Serve Deployment 会导入 Klein 的绑定应用，并接收与用户配置相同的工作流路径："

msgid ""
"The deployment runs that workflow as `__main__` and intercepts its call "
"to `execute()`. It extracts the marked functions without submitting the "
"workflow's ordinary Klein job, then executes the extracted chain for "
"incoming batches. The workflow file must therefore build the graph and "
"call `execute`; keep graph construction deterministic and avoid unrelated"
" process-wide side effects."
msgstr ""
"Deployment 将该工作流作为 `__main__` 运行，并拦截它对 `execute()` "
"的调用。它会提取已标记函数，而不提交工作流中的普通 Klein 作业，然后对传入批次执行提取出的 Chain。因此，工作流文件必须构建图并调用 "
"`execute`；请确保构图具有确定性，并避免无关的进程级副作用。"

msgid ""
"The job-side client must point at an already reachable proxy and "
"deployment:"
msgstr "作业端 Client 必须指向已经可达的 Proxy 和 Deployment："

msgid "Configuration reference"
msgstr "配置参考"

msgid "Key"
msgstr "键"

msgid "`serve.proxy-endpoints`"
msgstr "`serve.proxy-endpoints`"

msgid "Required comma-separated HTTP proxy base URLs."
msgstr "必填，以逗号分隔的 HTTP Proxy Base URL。"

msgid "`serve.deployment-name`"
msgstr "`serve.deployment-name`"

msgid "Required Serve deployment name."
msgstr "必填的 Serve Deployment 名称。"

msgid "`serve.route-prefix`"
msgstr "`serve.route-prefix`"

msgid "`/`"
msgstr "`/`"

msgid "Route prefix sent through the proxy API."
msgstr "通过 Proxy API 发送的路由前缀。"

msgid "`serve.client.num-cpus`"
msgstr "`serve.client.num-cpus`"

msgid "`1.0`"
msgstr "`1.0`"

msgid "CPU allocation for a multi-node region's embedded client."
msgstr "多节点区域嵌入式 Client 的 CPU 分配。"

msgid "`serve.client.concurrency`"
msgstr "`serve.client.concurrency`"

msgid "`1`"
msgstr "`1`"

msgid "Embedded client parallelism."
msgstr "嵌入式 Client 并行度。"

msgid "`serve.client.async-buffer-size`"
msgstr "`serve.client.async-buffer-size`"

msgid "`100`"
msgstr "`100`"

msgid "Maximum asynchronous buffered work."
msgstr "异步缓冲工作的最大数量。"

msgid "`serve.client.batch-timeout`"
msgstr "`serve.client.batch-timeout`"

msgid "`5`"
msgstr "`5`"

msgid "Proxy batch timeout in seconds."
msgstr "以秒为单位的 Proxy 批次超时。"

msgid "`serve.client.batch-size`"
msgstr "`serve.client.batch-size`"

msgid "`2`"
msgstr "`2`"

msgid "Proxy request batch size."
msgstr "Proxy 请求批次大小。"

msgid "`serve.client.max-attempts`"
msgstr "`serve.client.max-attempts`"

msgid "`30`"
msgstr "`30`"

msgid "Maximum HTTP request attempts."
msgstr "HTTP 请求最大尝试次数。"

msgid "`serve.client.slow-request-warning`"
msgstr "`serve.client.slow-request-warning`"

msgid "`60`"
msgstr "`60`"

msgid "Seconds before one slow-request warning."
msgstr "发出一次慢请求警告前等待的秒数。"

msgid "`serve.client.http-timeout`"
msgstr "`serve.client.http-timeout`"

msgid "`300`"
msgstr "`300`"

msgid "Total logical request timeout across retries and backoff, in seconds."
msgstr "包括重试和退避在内的逻辑请求总超时时间，单位为秒。"

msgid "`serve.client.http-connect-timeout`"
msgstr "`serve.client.http-connect-timeout`"

msgid "HTTP connect timeout in seconds."
msgstr "以秒为单位的 HTTP 连接超时。"

msgid "`serve.client.http-limit-per-host`"
msgstr "`serve.client.http-limit-per-host`"

msgid "Per-host connection limit."
msgstr "每个 Host 的连接数限制。"

msgid "`serve.client.http-connection-limit`"
msgstr "`serve.client.http-connection-limit`"

msgid "Total connection limit."
msgstr "总连接数限制。"

msgid "`serve.client.retry-backoff-max`"
msgstr "`serve.client.retry-backoff-max`"

msgid "`3.0`"
msgstr "`3.0`"

msgid "Maximum randomized exponential backoff; runtime-capped at 10 seconds."
msgstr "随机指数退避上限；运行时最高限制为 10 秒。"

msgid ""
"For a single marked operator, the proxy inherits that operator's CPU, "
"concurrency, batch size, and timeout. A multi-operator region uses the "
"`serve.client.*` resource and batching values. All keys also appear in "
"the [complete configuration reference](../configuration-reference.md), "
"including accepted configuration sources and precedence."
msgstr ""
"对于单个已标记 Operator，Proxy 会继承该 Operator 的 CPU、并发度、批次大小和超时。多 Operator 区域使用 "
"`serve.client.*` 资源和批处理值。所有键也会出现在[完整配置参考](../configuration-"
"reference.md)中，其中包括接受的配置来源和优先级。"

msgid "Requests, retries, and operations"
msgstr "请求、重试与运维"

msgid ""
"The proxy JSON-encodes NumPy batches, chooses among configured endpoints,"
" and reuses one request ID across retries. Connection errors, timeouts, "
"HTTP 408, 429, 502, 503, and 504 are retryable; other HTTP failures stop "
"retrying. The configured HTTP timeout is one total budget for the logical"
" call, including all attempts and backoff. Because a remote deployment "
"can finish a request before the client observes a failure, functions "
"should be deterministic and free of non-idempotent side effects."
msgstr ""
"Proxy 会对 NumPy 批次进行 JSON 编码，从已配置端点中选择一个，并在多次重试中复用同一请求 ID。连接错误、超时以及 HTTP "
"408、429、502、503 和 504 可以重试；其他 HTTP 失败会停止重试。配置的 HTTP "
"超时是一次逻辑调用的总预算，包含所有尝试和退避。由于远程部署可能在客户端观察到失败前已经完成请求，函数应具有确定性，且不包含非幂等副作用。"

msgid ""
"The deployment can optionally validate the `rayservice` request header "
"when the `RAY_SERVICE_NAME` environment variable is set. Monitor Serve "
"request duration and failure metrics through "
"[Observability](../observability.md), and protect the proxy endpoint with"
" the authentication and network policy expected by your environment."
msgstr ""
"设置 `RAY_SERVICE_NAME` 环境变量后，Deployment 可以选择验证 `rayservice` 请求 "
"Header。请通过[可观测性](../observability.md)监控 Serve "
"请求耗时和失败指标，并使用环境所要求的身份验证和网络策略保护 Proxy Endpoint。"

msgid ""
"Use Klein for Ray Redis value lookups, missing-key filters, and buffered "
"output."
msgstr "使用 Klein for Ray Redis 值 Lookup、缺失键过滤和缓冲输出。"

msgid "Redis"
msgstr "Redis"

msgid ""
"The Redis integration enriches or filters records in batch and streaming "
"pipelines and writes keyed values through a native streaming sink. "
"Install it with `python -m pip install \"ray-klein[redis]\"`."
msgstr ""
"Redis 集成可在批处理和流处理 Pipeline 中扩充或过滤记录，并通过原生流处理 Sink 写入键值。使用 `python -m pip "
"install \"ray-klein[redis]\"` 安装。"

msgid "Configure connections"
msgstr "配置连接"

msgid "`RedisConnectionConfig` is immutable and shared by lookups and output:"
msgstr "`RedisConnectionConfig` 不可变，并由 Lookup 和输出共享："

msgid "Meaning and constraint"
msgstr "含义与约束"

msgid "`host`"
msgstr "`host`"

msgid "Non-empty hostname or address."
msgstr "非空 Hostname 或地址。"

msgid "`port`"
msgstr "`port`"

msgid "`6379`"
msgstr "`6379`"

msgid "Integer from 1 through 65535."
msgstr "1 至 65535 之间的整数。"

msgid "`database`"
msgstr "`database`"

msgid "`0`"
msgstr "`0`"

msgid "Non-negative database number."
msgstr "非负数据库编号。"

msgid "`username`"
msgstr "`username`"

msgid "Optional ACL username."
msgstr "可选 ACL 用户名。"

msgid "`password`"
msgstr "`password`"

msgid "Optional password; omitted from object representation."
msgstr "可选密码；对象表示中会省略。"

msgid "`max_connections`"
msgstr "`max_connections`"

msgid "`10`"
msgstr "`10`"

msgid "Positive per-operator connection-pool capacity."
msgstr "每个 Operator 的正数连接池容量。"

msgid "`timeout`"
msgstr "`timeout`"

msgid "5 seconds"
msgstr "5 秒"

msgid "Positive connect and socket timeout."
msgstr "正数连接和 Socket 超时。"

msgid "`max_retries`"
msgstr "`max_retries`"

msgid "Non-negative Redis client retry count."
msgstr "非负 Redis Client 重试次数。"

msgid "`max_retry_delay`"
msgstr "`max_retry_delay`"

msgid "10 seconds"
msgstr "10 秒"

msgid "Positive exponential-backoff cap."
msgstr "正数指数退避上限。"

msgid "`connection_options`"
msgstr "`connection_options`"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "`{}`"
msgstr "`{}`"

msgid "Additional `BlockingConnectionPool` arguments."
msgstr "额外的 `BlockingConnectionPool` 参数。"

msgid ""
"Each operator instance creates and owns its connection pool. Use a secret"
" manager or runtime environment for credentials rather than committing a "
"password in pipeline source."
msgstr ""
"每个 Operator 实例都会创建并拥有自己的连接池。请使用 Secret Manager 或运行时环境提供凭据，而不要在 Pipeline "
"源码中提交密码。"

msgid "Enrich records"
msgstr "扩充记录"

msgid ""
"Pass the callable class and its constructor arguments to `map` so each "
"worker owns its Redis client:"
msgstr "将 Callable 类及其构造参数传给 `map`，使每个 Worker 都拥有自己的 Redis Client："

msgid ""
"`RedisValueLookup` supports `STRING`, `HASH`, `LIST`, and `SET`. Its "
"options are `key_prefix`, key `delimiter` (default `:`), optional hash "
"fields, and `result_field` (default `redis_value`). Redis byte responses "
"are decoded as UTF-8. A missing string returns `None`; selected missing "
"hash fields also become `None`."
msgstr ""
"`RedisValueLookup` 支持 `STRING`、`HASH`、`LIST` 和 `SET`。其选项包括 `key_prefix`、键"
" `delimiter`（默认 `:`）、可选 Hash 字段和 `result_field`（默认 `redis_value`）。Redis "
"字节响应会按 UTF-8 解码。缺失的 String 返回 `None`；选中的缺失 Hash 字段也会变为 `None`。"

msgid ""
"Batch-enabled transforms pipeline multiple non-transactional reads. "
"Streaming transforms issue one logical lookup per record. A Redis error "
"is recorded and raised so the normal task retry policy can apply."
msgstr ""
"支持批处理的 Transform 会通过 Pipeline 执行多次非事务读取。流处理 Transform 对每条记录发起一次逻辑 "
"Lookup。Redis 错误会被记录并抛出，以便应用常规 Task 重试策略。"

msgid "Keep only missing keys"
msgstr "仅保留缺失键"

msgid ""
"`RedisMissingKeyFilter` retains a record only when its extracted, "
"optionally prefixed key does not exist:"
msgstr "仅当提取出的键（可带前缀）不存在时，`RedisMissingKeyFilter` 才会保留记录："

msgid ""
"The filter supports both execution modes and pipelines `EXISTS` calls in "
"a batch-enabled operator. A lookup followed by another client write is "
"not an atomic check-and-set; concurrent producers can race."
msgstr ""
"该 Filter 支持两种执行模式，并在支持批处理的 Operator 中通过 Pipeline 执行 `EXISTS` 调用。Lookup "
"后由另一个 Client 写入并不是原子 check-and-set；并发 Producer 可能发生竞争。"

msgid "Write keyed values"
msgstr "写入键值"

msgid "Sink configuration"
msgstr "Sink 配置"

msgid "`RedisSinkConfig` field"
msgstr "`RedisSinkConfig` 字段"

msgid "`data_type`"
msgstr "`data_type`"

msgid "`STRING`"
msgstr "`STRING`"

msgid "`STRING`, `HASH`, `SET`, or `LIST`."
msgstr "`STRING`、`HASH`、`SET` 或 `LIST`。"

msgid "`key_prefix`"
msgstr "`key_prefix`"

msgid "Optional non-empty namespace prefix."
msgstr "可选的非空命名空间前缀。"

msgid "`delimiter`"
msgstr "`delimiter`"

msgid "`:`"
msgstr "`:`"

msgid "Non-empty prefix/key separator."
msgstr "非空的前缀/键分隔符。"

msgid "`ttl`"
msgstr "`ttl`"

msgid "Positive expiration duration applied after replacement."
msgstr "替换后应用的正数过期时长。"

msgid "Positive Redis pipeline batch size."
msgstr "正数 Redis Pipeline 批次大小。"

msgid "`flush_interval`"
msgstr "`flush_interval`"

msgid "1 second"
msgstr "1 秒"

msgid "Positive maximum buffering interval."
msgstr "正数最大缓冲间隔。"

msgid "`buffer_capacity`"
msgstr "`buffer_capacity`"

msgid "`5000`"
msgstr "`5000`"

msgid "Bounded buffer capacity; at least `batch_size`."
msgstr "有界缓冲区容量；至少为 `batch_size`。"

msgid ""
"`write_redis` also accepts `num_cpus`, `num_gpus`, `concurrency`, "
"operator `batch_size`, `batch_timeout` (default 3 seconds), and `name`. "
"The operator batch size controls how Klein delivers records to the sink; "
"the identically named `RedisSinkConfig.batch_size` controls the sink's "
"internal Redis pipeline."
msgstr ""
"`write_redis` 还接受 `num_cpus`、`num_gpus`、`concurrency`、Operator "
"`batch_size`、`batch_timeout`（默认 3 秒）和 `name`。Operator 批次大小控制 Klein 向 Sink"
" 交付记录的方式；同名的 `RedisSinkConfig.batch_size` 控制 Sink 内部 Redis Pipeline。"

msgid ""
"The sink uses `SET` for strings. It transactionally replaces hashes, "
"lists, and sets using `DEL` followed by `HSET`, `RPUSH`, or `SADD`; an "
"empty collection leaves the key deleted. Repeating the same replacement "
"is idempotent and list order is preserved."
msgstr ""
"Sink 对字符串使用 `SET`。它通过先执行 `DEL`，再执行 `HSET`、`RPUSH` 或 `SADD`，以事务方式替换 "
"Hash、List 和 Set；空集合会使键保持已删除状态。重复执行相同替换是幂等的，并会保留 List 顺序。"

msgid "Delivery guarantees and limits"
msgstr "交付保证与限制"

msgid ""
"Redis output is native streaming-only and automatically makes the overall"
" job streaming. The sink flushes at a checkpoint barrier, but Redis "
"mutations happen before checkpoint durability and are not a Klein two-"
"phase commit. Delivery is therefore **at-least-once**. Deterministic "
"replacement makes an identical replay idempotent per key, but concurrent "
"writers, non-deterministic values, and cross-key ordering can still "
"change the result."
msgstr ""
"Redis 输出仅支持原生流处理，并会自动使整个作业采用流处理。Sink 会在检查点 Barrier 处刷新，但 Redis "
"变更发生在检查点持久化之前，并不属于 Klein 两阶段提交。因此，交付具有 **at-least-once** "
"语义。确定性替换使相同重放对每个键幂等，但并发 Writer、非确定性值和跨键顺序仍可能改变结果。"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Redis has no built-in Table DDL factory. Use the DataStream API or "
"implement a [custom TableFactory](custom.md). Connector metrics and retry"
" logs are described in [Observability](../observability.md); API types "
"are listed in the {doc}`Redis API reference <../api/redis>`."
msgstr ""
"Redis 没有内置 Table DDL Factory。请使用 DataStream API，或实现[自定义 "
"TableFactory](custom.md)。Connector "
"指标和重试日志请参阅[可观测性](../observability.md)；API 类型请参阅 {doc}`Redis API reference"
" <../api/redis>`。"

msgid "Read continuous Apache RocketMQ topics with Klein for Ray."
msgstr "使用 Klein for Ray 读取连续 Apache RocketMQ topic。"

msgid "RocketMQ"
msgstr "RocketMQ"

msgid ""
"Klein reads Apache RocketMQ topics as unbounded `DataStream` inputs "
"through the official remoting-protocol Python client. The connector "
"supports clustering and broadcasting consumers, Tag expressions, orderly "
"callbacks, ACL credentials, SSL, client consume threads, and Ray source "
"parallelism."
msgstr ""
"Klein 通过官方 remoting-protocol Python Client，将 Apache RocketMQ topic 读取为无界 "
"`DataStream` 输入。该 Connector 支持 clustering 和 broadcasting Consumer、Tag "
"表达式、顺序回调、ACL 凭据、SSL、Client 消费线程和 Ray Source 并行度。"

msgid "Install"
msgstr "安装"

msgid ""
"`rocketmq-client-python` wraps the native `librocketmq` library. Install "
"a compatible `librocketmq` on every Ray worker, or use a client wheel "
"that bundles it. This connector targets remoting-protocol RocketMQ "
"deployments; it is not a RocketMQ 5 gRPC SimpleConsumer implementation."
msgstr ""
"`rocketmq-client-python` 封装原生 `librocketmq` 库。请在每个 Ray Worker 上安装兼容的 "
"`librocketmq`，或使用已捆绑该库的 Client Wheel。此 Connector 面向 remoting-protocol "
"RocketMQ 部署；它不是 RocketMQ 5 gRPC SimpleConsumer 实现。"

msgid "Read a topic"
msgstr "读取 topic"

msgid ""
"In clustering mode, all source subtasks join the same consumer group and "
"RocketMQ distributes messages among them. Set `concurrency` to the "
"desired number of Ray source subtasks. Broadcasting mode requires "
"`concurrency=1`; otherwise every source subtask would emit its own copy."
msgstr ""
"在 clustering 模式下，所有 Source Subtask 都会加入同一个消费组，RocketMQ 在它们之间分发消息。请将 "
"`concurrency` 设置为所需的 Ray Source Subtask 数量。broadcasting 模式要求 "
"`concurrency=1`；否则每个 Source Subtask 都会发出自己的副本。"

