msgid "Delivery and recovery"
msgstr "交付与恢复"

msgid ""
"The Python SDK exposes a PushConsumer callback and does not expose "
"partition assignment, seek, or checkpoint-controlled offset commits. "
"Klein copies each native message into a bounded queue and returns "
"`CONSUME_SUCCESS` only after the source thread has emitted the record and"
" force-flushed its local transport batch into the next task. If emission "
"fails or the source is cancelled first, it returns `RECONSUME_LATER`."
msgstr ""
"Python SDK 公开 PushConsumer 回调，但不公开分区分配、seek 或由检查点控制的 offset 提交。Klein "
"会将每条原生消息复制到有界队列中，并且只在 Source 线程发出记录、且将本地传输批次强制刷新到下一个 Task 后返回 "
"`CONSUME_SUCCESS`。如果发出失败或 Source 先被取消，则返回 `RECONSUME_LATER`。"

msgid ""
"RocketMQ consumer-group progress is therefore the source recovery "
"boundary, not Klein's checkpoint metadata. A full job rollback can lose "
"records that the broker acknowledged after the last durable Klein "
"checkpoint. Use an idempotent downstream sink and retain message IDs when"
" deduplication matters. Workloads that require checkpoint-coordinated "
"source offsets should use the Kafka connector or a custom pull-based "
"`SourceFunction`."
msgstr ""
"因此，RocketMQ 消费组进度是 Source 恢复边界，而不是 Klein 检查点元数据。完整作业回滚可能丢失 Broker 在最近一次持久"
" Klein 检查点之后已确认的记录。如果去重很重要，请使用幂等的下游 Sink 并保留消息 ID。需要由检查点协调 Source offset "
"的工作负载应使用 Kafka Connector，或自定义基于 Pull 的 `SourceFunction`。"

